{"tid":1564431,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"新戰線-香港人要主導聯合全世界反中共，反Chinazi","createTime":"2019-09-12T18:17:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T01:03:13.000Z","uid":286864,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"70142349a8d12a83177e698c752eca15a73e61c1","tid":1564431,"uid":286864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T18:17:15.000Z","msg":"美國民主法案係主打，但都唔好忽略要拉攏其他國家支持，尤其係同中國有潛在或實際利益既國家，例如<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">德國、法國</span></strong>等歐盟國家係我地之前少留意既領域，而不少<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>東歐</strong></span>國家之前飽受蘇聯折磨，佢地都會同情我地，佢地不少又係原本一帶一路要拉攏既國家，所以有佢地既支持會對中共造成雙重打擊！<br />\n<br />\n香港要贏中共，就一定要有全世界支持，而剛好香港最大優勢就係具有國際視野，我地一定要好好運用本身優勢先可以有一線生機！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">國際反中共戰線，香港會係全世界既超級聯繫人！</span></span>"},{"pid":"07be05ec5aa3ff14b372e71876d2cfbdf26ba263","tid":1564431,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T18:17:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/QV6Mycc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQV6Mycc.jpg&h=35dfaea1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40319db4389c74921446644a0694eff16b91c45c","tid":1564431,"uid":251769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T18:17:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/REHv0jX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FREHv0jX.png&h=4961a981&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vSVp4MD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvSVp4MD.jpg&h=3d25b08e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QvwgVTi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQvwgVTi.jpg&h=88868b4f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3ZxWVTj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3ZxWVTj.png&h=651de955&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dc20eb6c7cbb81cbaa8c22